           <gco:CharacterString>The NAIP National Metadata Map contains USGS Quarter Quad and NAIP Seamline boundaries for every year NAIP imagery has been collected. Clicking on the map also makes available a number of metadata fields which describe the day, time, camera, aircraft, and location of NAIP collection.
